OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780413074
OL,3,CAlderney's #24 million runway revamp
OL,4,Cset for delays
OL,6,FPoliticians have warned that
OL,7,FAlderney's new runway could be delayed
OL,8,Fbeyond its 2027 target after the first
OL,9,Fkey target was missed.
OL,11,FThe island's airport has been repaired
OL,12,Fnumerous times in recent years, and
OL,13,F#24 million was allocated for the
OL,14,Fproject by the Guernsey government in
OL,15,FFebruary.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
