CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780413074
OL,3,CAlderney's #24 million runway revamp
OL,4,Cset for delays
OL,6,FBuilding works were planned to start
OL,7,Fin April 2027 and conclude in
OL,8,FDecember. According to the policy
OL,9,Fdocument published earlier this year,
OL,10,Fthe tender process should have been
OL,11,Fcompleted last month.
OL,13,FDespite that optimistic timeline,
OL,14,Fthere has still been no company
OL,15,Fselected to carry out the works.
OL,17,FThe government is working on
OL,18,Fcontingencies to mitigate disruption.
OL,19,FThat could include a bolstered ferry
OL,20,Fsurface and the use of a grass runway.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780413074
OL,3,CAlderney's #24 million runway revamp
OL,4,Cset for delays
OL,6,FMedical evacuations are expected to
OL,7,Fcontinue by helicopter and boat in the
OL,8,Fintervening period.
OL,10,FWhen the works do eventually take
OL,11,Fplace, the airport will be closed for
OL,12,Ffive months.
OL,14,FStates of Alderney Representative,
OL,15,FAlex Snowden, told ITV News: "The
OL,16,Fworst thing that could possibly happen
OL,17,Fis that we lost a whole year because,
OL,18,Funfortunately, the delays have crept
OL,19,Fin."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
