PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780413074
OL,3,CAlderney's #24 million runway revamp
OL,4,Cset for delays
OL,6,FThe construction window is dependent
OL,7,Fon weather conditions and, if delays
OL,8,Fcontinue further, politicians have
OL,9,Ftold ITV that construction may not
OL,10,Fstart until 2028.
OL,12,FThe current plans include resurfacing
OL,13,Fwork, lighting and drainage. They
OL,14,Fwould also widen the runway from 18 to
OL,15,F23 meters.
OL,17,FA previous plan to rebuild the runway
OL,18,Fand airport had been approved in 2022
OL,19,Fbut was cancelled when costs ballooned
OL,20,Fto #37 million.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
